{
  "stem": "311.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He made a living out of it in United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened-- he came to the United States, so he became a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was down in the Bronx.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One time I came home from California.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, hey, what's going on here?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Big write-up, you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My name on it, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "European [SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH] [LAUGHTER] But she said, oh, that-- that-- that-- that's how they want it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's how they wrote it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, my father moved from one section to-- or are we still supposed to talk about-- It's OK.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's alright, alright.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was an interesting sideline.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was interested.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, he was working for ARCO and had an accident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- then he collected-- how you call it?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When you have an accident, how you call this?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Workman's compensation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then on Grand Concourse, he-- he was-- he became a-- a regular [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] .",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And across the street, there-- there-- there was a court, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was 161st Street.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a court-- a big court of the Bronx is on Grand Concourse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The judges, the lawyers, they used to come into the shul.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was learning [INAUDIBLE] with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I will never understand.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father always had a pocket full with money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow, he did better than anybody, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was the black sheep in the whole family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I just-- I just didn't-- I have nothing against it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I love it very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have a very-- I have a respect for all the rabbis for everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It just didn't go with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it just--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but you know-- but--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Krakow had-- you have to understand that Krakow had about 60,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
